  "title": "\n      APP_ROOT_SCOPE\n    ",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          \n            {\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 1,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\",\n              \"name\": \"API\"\n            }\n          }\n            ,{\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 2,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\",\n              \"name\": \"@angular/core\"\n            }\n          }\n            ,{\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 3,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE\",\n              \"name\": \"APP_ROOT_SCOPE\"\n            }\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n      </script>\n    \n      \n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a>\n    \n      /\n      <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    \n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">experimental</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    <h1 id=\"app_root_scope\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#app_root_scope\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>\n      APP_ROOT_SCOPE\n    </h1>\n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n      <a href=\"api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#\"><label class=\"raised page-label\"><i class=\"material-icons\">mode_edit</i>suggest edits</label></a>\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.5/packages/core/src/di/scope.ts#L27-L27\"><label class=\"raised page-label\"><i class=\"material-icons\">code</i>view source</label></a>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ROOT_SCOPE</a>: any;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Description</h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">A scope which targets the root injector.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">When specified as the <code>scope</code> parameter to <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a></code> or <code><a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a></code>, this special\nscope indicates the provider for the service or token being configured belongs in the root\ninjector. This is loosely equivalent to the convention of having a <code>forRoot()</code> static\nfunction within a module that configures the provider, and expecting users to only import that\nmodule via its <code>forRoot()</code> function in the root injector.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#\n - api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#app_root_scope\n - api/core/APP_ROOT_SCOPE#description\n - api/core/Injectable\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.5/packages/core/src/di/scope.ts#L27-L27\n-->"
